comment._content: While operating for Aviastar-TU this particular aircraft, Tupolev Tu-204-100, registration RA-64011 (c/n 1450741364011), would crash in March 2010 while landing at Domodedovo Airport, just outside of Moscow. Of the eight people aboard, four suffered serious injuries, and four less serious injuries. Fortunately, there were no fatalities. The accident is detailed here: en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aviastar-TU_Flight_1906
